Subject: [PATCH] docs: fix documentation inconsistencies
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Generate-code-from-TypeSpec.md: fix incorrect pnpm install command
  (`npm install -g @pnpm` → `npm install -g pnpm`; the package name has
  no @ prefix)

- golden-testing-commands.md: update outdated test script names
  (`unit-test:node` and `integration-test:node` are no longer used;
  modern packages use `test:node`)

- next-generation-quickstart.md: fix missing @ scope prefix
  (`azure/arm-resources` → `@azure/arm-resources`)

- resolve-pnpm-lock-merge-conflict.md: fix missing path separator in
  one-liner shell command (`git rev-parse --show-toplevel`pnpm-lock.yaml
  → `git rev-parse --show-toplevel`/pnpm-lock.yaml)

- steps-after-generations.md: remove incorrect global dev-tool install
  instruction (`npm install -g common/tools/dev-tool` is unnecessary
  because `npx dev-tool` works directly from any workspace package
  directory; the following line already uses npx)

Co-authored-by: Copilot <223556219+Copilot@users.noreply.github.com>
